review_blob: This beer is so smooth its remarkable. I had it at the tasting room and saw so many people enjoying this beer that were young and old, male and female. The beer is so tasty and smooth it sneaks up on you quick with the high Alcohol so you never know what hit you.

The ABV was actually 3.8 and 100 IBUs. A session IPA that actually huge flavor like a West Coast IPA well balanced with malt. Hard to believe a session this low in ABV has this much aroma and flavor. Perfect summer session beer. I wont need to go to sleep after a few of them.
